{{version030}}
{{flavour|Violently collapses a nearby simulacrum into a large mass of ice, which explodes on impact. The ice affects even cold-resistant creatures somewhat, due to the strong impact and cutting edges.}}

'''Seracfall''' is a monster-only spell which destroys a [[simulacrum]] to launch a 3x3 explosion at the target. Like [[iceblast]], it deals 50% irresistible [[cold]] damage that never misses. This spell requires a simulacrum in the user's [[line of sight]] to be cast, and it must be friendly to the caster (i.e. it cannot use your own simulacrum against you).

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*Prior to [[0.30]], Seracfall's damage was 40% resistible (60% irresistible).
*Seracfall was added in [[0.28]].

[[Category: Monster spells]]
